# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __iand__, __ior__, __ixor__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# All eighteen values are false. decimal.Decimal has no bitwise operators at
# all: waves 661/665 confirmed __and__/__or__/__xor__ and __rand__/__ror__/__rxor__
# are all absent from decimal.Decimal.__dict__. The in-place variants
# __iand__, __ior__, __ixor__ are likewise absent: bitwise AND, OR, and XOR
# have no meaning for arbitrary-precision decimal arithmetic.
# Consistent with waves 666/667/668: no in-place operators present in
# decimal.Decimal.__dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

